Package entity

Class Cinema

java.lang.Object
entity.Cinema
public class Cinema extends Object
A Cinema which belongs to a Cineplex. with attributes of Cinema Code, Hall number, Cineplex, CinemaClass to represent the Class(Standard/Platinum), Showtimes of this cinema, which may have many showtimes in this cinema and SeatingLayout
